block content
  h1 Welcome to the Homepage

  p This is the index page for our Express server with Pug templates.

  // Part 4 – Button with Bootstrap styling
  button(type="button", class="btn btn-primary", onclick="faster()") Sample Button

  // Part 4 – Div for interaction
  div#faster add in extra

  // Part 6 – Link to journals page
  p
    a(href="/journals") → View Journal Results

  // JavaScript block
  script.
    let value = 1;
    let amt = 2;

